{# description: Generates a structured log entry summarizing a sent email interaction for CRM notes #}

Generate a structured CRM note summarizing this sent email interaction.

RULES:
- summary_text must not contain email addresses, phone numbers, or personal contact details
- topic_tags: 1–4 short lowercase tags describing the subject matter (e.g., "quote", "lead-time", "tech-support")
- next_action: one of: NONE | FOLLOW_UP_7D | FOLLOW_UP_14D | AWAIT_RESPONSE | ESCALATE
- Do not include draft body content verbatim — summarize only
- crm_note_text must be under 200 words

THREAD ID: {{ thread_id }}
CATEGORY: {{ category }}
SENT AT: {{ sent_at_utc }}
RUN ID: {{ run_id }}

--- ORIGINAL EMAIL SUMMARY ---
Subject Hash: {{ subject_hash }}
Sender: {{ sender_hash }}
Draft Word Count: {{ draft_word_count }}
Flags: {{ flags | join(', ') if flags else 'none' }}
--- END SUMMARY ---
